doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        title Atrox's Online-Poker

    body
        div(route="/").route.active
            h1 WELCOME TO ATROX'S ONLINE-POKER-SITE
            label(for="name-input") Your nickname:
            input#name-input(type="text", name="name", placeholder="enter your nickname, please")
            
            button#join-room-btn Join Room
            button#create-room-btn Create Room

            #cn-get-roomid
                label(for="id-input") Room-ID:
                input#id-input(type="text", name="id", placeholder="please enter the room id")
                input(type="submit", value="go to room").submit-id-btn
        

        div(route="/lobby").route
            form#settings
                label(for="i-money") So viel Chips erhält jeder Spieler zu Anfang:
                input(type="number", name="initMoney", id="i-money", value="100" required)
                label(for="i-min-bet") Um so viel muss man mindestens erhöhen + Blind setzen:
                input(type="number", name="minBet", id="i-min-bet", value="5" required)
                label(for="i-min-delay") Nach so vielen verstrichenen Sekunden ohne Aktion, wird ein Spieler als inaktiv gesetzt:
                input(type="number", name="minDelay", id="i-min-delay", value="60" required) 
                input(type="submit", value="Start")
            
            ul#lobby


        div(route="/game").route
            


        